high_descs: Walk towards the wall, then turn left and begin walking across the room, hang a right and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the sponge off of the counter in front of the sink.
Turn left and walk forward, then hang a left and walk over to the counter and turn right then walk up to the oven.
Put the sponge in the metal pot that is on the back left burner of the stove.
Pick up the metal pot with the sponge in it.
Walk over to the round white table that is in the corner of the room behind you.
Put the metal pot with the sponge in it on the round white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a metal pot with a sponge in it on a round white table.

high_descs: Turn left then walk towards the door, turn right then walk towards the sink.
Pick up the sponge in front of the sink on the counter top.
Turn all the way around then head towards the counter, then right towards the stove.
Put the sponge into the pan located on the left back burner.
Pick up the pan with the sponge in it.
Turn all the way around then walk towards the wall, then head right then walk towards the table against the wall.
Place the pan onto the table behind the roll of paper towels.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan with a sponge in it onto the table.

high_descs: Turn left, move to the counter, turn right, move to the sink.
Pick up the sponge on the counter in front of the sink.
Turn around, bring the sponge to the stove on the right.
Put the sponge in the pot at the back of the stove.
Pick up the pot with sponge on the stove.
Turn around, bring the pot with sponge around the counter to the white, round table in the corner on the other side of the kitchen.
Put the bowl with sponge on the round table.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with sponge in it, on the round table.
